cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

The paper deals with image classification using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of self-taught learning and dictionary learning also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of multiple layers and classification algorithms also suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the use of remote sensing data suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
